725836f-a.title: Queens: 124th Street - 14th Avenue
725836f-a.text:
124th Street, west side, between 14th and 15th Avenues
showing St. Fidelis Ronman Catholio Church. View 2 is north
across 15th Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  March 16, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
